HEADWORD: Delaware
<hw>Del"a*ware</hw> <pr>(d⟦ecr⟧l"⟦adot⟧*w⟦acir⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>one of the thirteen original states of the United
States of America.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An American grape, with compact
bunches of small, amber-colored berries, sweet and of a good
flavor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Delawarean</ent>⟦br⟧
